Pros:. Have it since Jan 2008. I currently own 37 BR movies, rent aprox 20 movies, NO problem at all. Excellent resolution, excellent sound. Great player. 
Cons:. Could be a little slow sometimes,.. 
Summary:. great player for the price. If you keep it updated, you won have any problems.. 

