Summary:. This is one of the better Blu-ray players out there. The color is crisp and the load time is fairly quick. I love it. I would definitely buy it for my 1st Blu-ray player. You can download the firmware, but it takes awhile over 30 minutes or have Samsung send you the firmware disk before you purchase it, or go to their website. Overall it plays like a gem.. 

