Summary:. This player was offered free with a new HDTV. The picture quality is amazing but it lacks some key features.. 1st, it has no resume play! So if you don't like watching a movie in all one sitting you lose your place &#38; get stuck watching unskippable introductory warnings, previews, etc. This is totally unacceptable, even the cheapest of DVD players has resume play after shutting off the power.. No time options either. In fact it doesn't even display total running time for the movie, let alone count down mode.. Why basic things people come to expect from disc players are not present is a mystery &#38; great disappointment to me. Good thing the player was free or I wouldn't keep it.. 

