Summary:. just bought mine on line from Best Buy $399.00=7 free Blu-ray DVD's.- I called Samsung and they are sending a disc to update the unit.They are having alot of complaints about not being compatible, skipping, shutting off and reading certain DVD's. Hopefully their update will fix these problems. Should of bought the Panasonic!. 

