Summary:. The 1400 is the blu ray player with more problems in the moment.. I upgrade to 1.2 firmware and the problems still here, many titles has reproduction problems, 1080p/24 not played fine, some times dont turn on, "Welcome" stay forever.... The 1400 is the worst buy in BR Player, buy a PS3, works perfect, fast, constant upgrades, BD1.1 and future 2.0, play every titles fine, with no problem.... 1400 is a poor, very very poor player, I dont buy a Samsung product NEVER MORE!!!. 

