Pros:. Picture detail is good. 
Cons:. Customer Service---very very bad one of the worst I ever had to deal with...They promise you a cal back and never do.... they say they are going to send you a new "Frirmware" Disk and never sent it... 
Summary:. I rented a new DVD DISTRICT 9 from Blockbuster... was not able to watch it on my Blu-Ray, due to the fact that it not being up to date...It was purchased in 2008... I called Blockbuster to complain and I was told I needed to upgrade the Blu-Ray. I called Samsung and was told to try to download it off their site, I didn't have a CDR that was needed for this. They offered to send me a CD ith the Firmware Upgrade on it.... well when I got it 2 weeks later it was cracked... In the meantime I went out and bought a DVD R to download the Firmware, it did not work.... all this being done with customer service on the tele.... I tried it 5 TIMES with no luck. After calling them back again and getting a person from another country that I was not able to understand, (out of 10 calls to Samsung, I was only able to understand 2 Americans).... I was told that they would expidte a new DVD FIRMWARE for me to upgrade... that was 6 days ago... So last nite(2-5-10) I called and I was told it was never sent....he would send it out on Monday.. I asked to speak to a supervisor and was told they would call me back in 24 to 48 hours... that was the second time I was told this by a customer service person....the first time I never got a call back, after the person said he was "putting the note on her desk as we speak"... II will never, never buy a Samsung product again, the customer service is not consumer friendly.! I am 55 yrs old... I have dealt with customer service people for all types of issues over the years....I have never felt like writting until this episode.... I think they seem to forget who the CUSTOMER is...I do not expect to get any where with this or do I expect a call from Samsung... I am just letting other consumers know to beware of Samsung. There I vented and said my peace!. 

